item.title: Multiple people on private plane that crashed into San Diego neighborhood are dead, authorities say
item.description: Authorities say a private jet crashed into military housing in San Diego during foggy weather, igniting cars parked along a suburban neighborhood block and killing multiple people on board the plane.
